a = ChromeCookies(db=chrome_db)
a.add_cookie('example.com', 'test_name3', 'test_value')
a.delete_cookie('example.com', 'test_name3')
conn = sqlite3.Connection(chrome_db)
cur = conn.cursor()
cur.execute('SELECT * FROM {0}'.format(a.table_name))
res = cur.fetchall()
try:
    assert len(res) == 0
finally:
    conn.close()
